    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>pizza bases</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>sweetcorn purée</strong> between the <strong>pizza bases </strong>and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p><p>Top with your<strong> diced chorizo</strong> and <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> and return the tray[s] to the oven for 12-15 min or until the cheese has melted and the bases are crisp – these are your <strong>chorizo & sweetcorn pizzas</strong></p>",
