    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pizzas are cooking, strip your <strong>coriander leaves</strong> from their stalks, discard the stalks</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
