    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chorizo & sweetcorn pizzas</strong> with the <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish the pizzas with the <strong>coriander leaves</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>and <strong>chilli oil </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Drizzle the salad with your <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>and a little <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
